Package: openmc
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}
Replaces: openmc (<< 0.7.0)
Description: Open source Monte Carlo neutron transport code
 OpenMC is a 3D constructive solid geometry, continuous-energy Monte Carlo
 neutron transport code written in Fortran 2008. Particle interaction data is
 based on ACE format cross sections, and user input is given in an XML format.